    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away! If you're looking for something reliable that still looks great and drives even better, this is definitely the one for you. I've taken great care of it and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
