    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts a linear power band and exceptional throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a factory M-Variable differential lock, providing superb traction through the corners. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the primary technical concerns of the chassis. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, and the braking system offers firm pedal feel with minimal fade. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical integrity remains uncompromising for the serious driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
