    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between premium performance and everyday utility. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, it offers a smooth, responsive drive that feels remarkably solid on the road. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, showing only the minor, honest signs of careful use consistent with a well-cared-for vehicle. Inside, the cabin remains a clean and comfortable sanctuary; the upholstery is free of significant wear, and all electronic features\u2014from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring it is mechanically sound and ready for the miles ahead. This is a dependable, high-quality choice for a buyer who values both longevity and a refined driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
