    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This specimen has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring a driving experience that balances performance with sophisticated poise. With its robust mechanical history and well-preserved interior, it represents an outstanding opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking quality without compromise. Experience the assurance of a vehicle that has been curated for longevity and consistent excellence.",
      "price": 36800.0,
