    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been absolutely wonderful to me. It's in really solid shape and has been well-maintained over the years, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It drives smoothly and is super reliable for both city errands and longer highway trips. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
