      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical vitals are robust: the VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. It retains its factory-spec limited-slip differential and communicative hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains visceral with instantaneous throttle response and a linear power band. A well-sorted chassis makes this an ideal candidate for the serious driving enthusiast.",
